Directory /smart/Doc/howto
        Hints on how to do things in SMART.


admin           Being a database administer.  In particular, how to 
                set up a collection specification file.
debug
                How to use the trace facility to debug both
                spec files and procedures
defaults        Not really a how-to.  Contains the complete (as
                of beta release) default specification file with
                explanations of parameters and values.
examine         How to look at SMART database and retrieval files.
install.xx      How to install SMART Version XX
modify          How to add procedures to SMART.
retrieve        Examples of how to perform a retrieval run.
